Author: 0rangevanillac0ke0
Text: Do what you need to do to take care of yourself ❤️ Call someone if you need to. But I promise it’s ok. Breaking streaks sucks, I have a long steak on MFP I’m terrified to break. Also, lots of step counters don’t register every step so you probably did break 10k even if it didn’t count it. Tech is weird. But you’re trying and doing your best, I promise it will be ok and you aren’t a failure or anything bad ❤️
